COMMENT ON COLUMN JNITEBOOK.PAGE_WIDTH is '페이지 가로';
COMMENT ON COLUMN JNITEBOOK.PAGE_HEIGHT is '페이지 세로';
COMMENT ON COLUMN JNITEBOOK.THUMB_YN is '썸네일 여부';
COMMENT ON COLUMN JNITEBOOK.THUMB_AOTO_HIDE is '썸네일 숨기기';
COMMENT ON COLUMN JNITEBOOK.THUMB_WIDTH is '썸네일 가로';
COMMENT ON COLUMN JNITEBOOK.THUMB_HEIGHT is '썸네일 세로';
COMMENT ON COLUMN JNITEBOOK.SHARE_LINK is '링크주소';
COMMENT ON COLUMN JNITEBOOK.SHARE_TEXT is '메세지';
COMMENT ON COLUMN JNITEBOOK.SHARE_VIA is '소유주';
COMMENT ON COLUMN JNITEBOOK.ISDEL is '삭제여부';
